snippet: The mother of three children killed when a carjacked sport utility vehicle crashed into a group selling fruit on a Philadelphia street corner for a church fund-raiser has died.
abstract: Keisha Williams, mother of three children who were killed when a carjacked SUV crashed into church fund-raising group on Philadelphia street corner, dies after two weeks in critical condition.
lead_paragraph: The mother of three children killed when a carjacked sport utility vehicle crashed into a group selling fruit on a Philadelphia street corner for a church fund-raiser has died.

headline.main: Pennsylvania: Fourth Victim Dies After Carjacking
headline.print_headline: Pennsylvania: Fourth Victim Dies After Carjacking
